    gradient        background, text, overlay
    @supports       
        caniuse.com
        Vendor Prefix   

    shadow          box-shadow, text-shadow
        box-shadow  (x  y  blur  scale )        0 0 0 10px red;


    CSS Specificity
        tags    <    .class = [attribute]   <   #id     <   inline style    <    !important
    
    CSS variable declaration (inside :root)
        :root {
            --primary-color: #00aefd;
            --secondary-color: #ffa400;
        }
    
    child 
        geeksforgeeks.org/difference-between-first-child-and-first-of-type-selector-in-css/
            :first-child        the FIRST child of the parent
            :first-of-type      the first of its TYPE, of the parent (can comes 2nd, 3rd or 4th any place)
    
    CSS Selectors       + > ~
        w3schools.com/cssref/css_selectors.asp

    a-tag
        ^       starting with                       a[href^="https"
        $       ending with                         a[href$=".vn"]
        *       contain specific characters         a[href*="xyz"]

    p::first-letter
    p::first-line           
        only apply to semantic elements, not apply to <a>
        can : or :: (both works)

    transition
        property: color, background, border, .... default: all
        timer: 2s 3s
        easing: linear ease-in, ease-out, ease-in-out,
        cubic-bezier(0.075, 0.82, 0.165, 1)
    check more about cubic bezier:    https://cubic-bezier.com/ 
    Transition for :hover   --> must use 'transition' before using 'hover'

    :empty
        .boxed:empty {
            display: none;
        }